                      span.ks-name Lisa Morris
                    span.ks-date-created September 29, 2016
                  .ks-body
                    .ks-text
                      | Express Wi-Fi empowers entrepreneurs to build a business by providing their community with access to the internet. Facebook designed the technology, and local internet providers add the connectivity. Express Wi-Fi is part of our Internet.org initiative.
                  .ks-footer
                    .ks-block
                      span.ks-control(data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="Comment")
                        span.fa.fa-comment-o.ks-icon
                        span.ks-amount 12
                    .ks-block
                      span.ks-control(data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="Share")
